      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "LAYLA'S LILLY (3) ran a good time (22.62) winning a Grade 4/5 two back at this track but missed the frame latest finishing fourth at this track. With a good start should be able to take advantage of the low draw. Has the ability and looks a key chance here. ZIPPING BALBOA (2) broke from a low draw and filled a minor placing last start, beaten only 2 lengths (22.97) behind Sneaky Jade at this track. Ran one of the fastest times on the program last start despite finishing in the minors. Expecting another good run. NOT DEFINITE (7) returned a better run last time, finishing in the money (23.22) at this track behind Crimson Dynamo in a Mix 1/2/3. Has the early speed to land on the pace and can stick on. Leading chance. GO FORWARD ROCKY (4) placed two runs ago then again in the money last time when second (22.78) at this track in a Grade 4/5. Solid beginner and with a good start can find clear running from trap eight.",
